spec_data.Name: python-mozlog
spec_data.Description:
Mozlog is a Python package intended to simplify and standardize logs
in the Mozilla universe.  It wraps around Python's logging module and
provides some additional functionality.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sat 29 Jul 2017 02:06:34 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Robust log handling specialized for logging in the Mozilla universe
